# Equations (PHI_THK)

Add equation: heatS {
   Coupled: f
   Min iterations: 1
   Max iterations: 5
   Tolerance: 1e-6

   Conductivity: 1.0
   Source term: 0.0
   Density: 0.0

   Output: Spatial {
      Temperature: t
   }

   Output: Alias {
      Temperature: PHI_THK
   }

   LS type: CG
   {
      Preconditioner: FSILS
      Max iterations: 500
      Tolerance:      1D-6
   }

   Add BC: epi {
      Type: Dir
      Value: 1.0
      Zero out perimeter: f
   }

   Add BC: endo {
      Type: Dir
      Value: 0.0
      Zero out perimeter: f
   }
}
